OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPregnant soon after        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmiscarriage no more risky -
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstudy                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Contrary to current advice, getting    
OL,6, pregnant within a few months of an     
OL,7, abortion or a miscarriage does not     
OL,8, appear to be extra risky for the mum   
OL,9, and baby, say researchers who have     
OL,10, looked at recent real-life data.       
OL,12,FThe World Health Organization (WHO)    
OL,13,Frecommends at least a six-month gap.   
OL,15,FThis is to give the woman time to      
OL,16,Frecover.                               
OL,18,FBut a study in PLoS Medicine, analysing
OL,19,F72,000 conceptions, suggests couples   
OL,20,Fmight safely try sooner for a baby.    
